tags: i have two days off and dont know what to do
no wait actually ill be braiding bracelets
body:
So what now?

As we can see, things are going slow…no title drop, no star wars show, no official news, nothing.

Potential title drop dates:

  • Valentines’s Day [credit to @mytrash-mylife ♡♡] (this is a really good theory and it’d be bold of lf to do such a thing)
  • Anywhere between today and Celebration yet not when there is another movie trailer/teaser are scheduled to drop; eg; another Endgame tv spot. It seems that lf don’t like to share.
  • Star Wars Celebration 

Teasers and trailers are usually released at Celebration and not earlier. As long as John Boyega doesn’t post anything regarding his last day on set I’ll be sitting here practising my knitting and wait patiently. And oooooh since the bafta is on this coming weekend Adam might be filming this week as well……

Alternatively, it might have something to do with a certain tall, dark-haired, good-for-nothing flyboy, who went from passionately kissing her one moment to condescendingly ruffling her hair the next.
Either way, this is shaping up to be a long mission - for more reasons than one.
